	<section id="perls" class="gray-section">
		<div class="container link2top">
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-sm-7 col-sm-push-5">
					<h2>Perls</h2>

					<p class="lead">A pervasive learning platform that uses your interests and your context to suggest the best lesson to learn right now.</p>

					<p>Perls is a context-aware education platform with a mobile-first learning experience. Based on a user&rsquo;s learning goals and habits, plus their current activity, schedule, and location, Perls recommends lessons and helps the user develop positive learning strategies.</p>
					<p>I am the design lead and iPhone developer for Perls, which is an ongoing research project at SRI.</p>

