						<li class="active">Swipe through Perls&rsquo; top suggestions as cards. &ldquo;Here &amp; Now&rdquo; recommends lessons that are of immediate benefit (nearby, timely, due soon) or especially well-suited to your current activity (such as podcasts for your commute or a how-to manual at the office photocopier).</li>

						<li>If you&rsquo;re killing time in the checkout line, the &ldquo;Quick Pick&rdquo; list will find something you can learn in a few minutes and interrupt as needed.</li>

