						<li>Over time, Perls will learn more about your interests and study patterns. The occasional &ldquo;action card&rdquo; may suggest new goals (&ldquo;Interested in Augmented Reality?&rdquo;) or better habits (&ldquo;Better pick up the pace!&rdquo;).</li>

						<li>Your path through a topic is defined by your goal, level of interest, and current expertise. Perls boils this down to four simple options: Explore, Study, Master, and Stay Sharp. Once you make a choice, Perls can filter and sequence content to suit your path.</li>
